Simulation Model Software:

Unity (Formats e.g. OBJ, FBX, PLY)
-> via C# Deep Learning Strategies

Typical workflow to generate a 3D Model in unity:

1. Generate Video/Picture footage (overlap rate 60-80%) -> 80-90 Pictures for a range of 20-30m
2. Generate a 3D Model (structure model) on ODM
3. Download the folder with the object and the textures
4. Upload it on unity in a separate folder and drag the object into the scene
5. Create a Mesh Collider to set the base of the map
-> Further activities (hole creation, deep learning) 

